<script>
    (() => {
        const initMraid = (window) => {
            try {
                mraid;
            } catch {
                mraidConnect(window, false);
                return;
            }

            if (mraid.getState() === 'loading') {
                mraid.addEventListener('ready', () => {
                    mraidConnect(window, true);
                });
            } else {
                mraidConnect(window, true);
            }
        };

        const makeOptions = () => ({
            placementType: mraid.getPlacementType(),
            expandProperties: mraid.getExpandProperties(),
            orientationProperties: mraid.getOrientationProperties(),
            resizeProperties: mraid.getResizeProperties(),
            maxSize: mraid.getMaxSize(),
            features: {
                sms: mraid.supports('sms'),
                tel: mraid.supports('tel'),
                calendar: mraid.supports('calendar'),
                storePicture: mraid.supports('storePicture'),
                inlineVideo: mraid.supports('inlineVideo'),
            },
        });

        const mraidConnect = (eventSource, proxy) => {
            eventSource.postMessage({ event: 'init', data: proxy, options: proxy ? makeOptions() : undefined }, '*');

            if (proxy) {
                mraid.addEventListener('error', (message, action) => {
                    eventSource.postMessage({ event: 'error', data: { message, action, options: makeOptions() } }, '*');
                });

                mraid.addEventListener('sizeChange', (width, height) => {
                    eventSource.postMessage({ event: 'sizeChange', data: { width, height }, options: makeOptions() }, '*');
                });

                mraid.addEventListener('stateChange', (state) => {
                    eventSource.postMessage({ event: 'stateChange', data: state, options: makeOptions() }, '*');
                });

                mraid.addEventListener('viewableChange', (viewable) => {
                    eventSource.postMessage({ event: 'viewableChange', data: viewable, options: makeOptions() }, '*');
                });
            }
        };

        window.addEventListener('message', (event) => {
            if (event.source !== window.frames.wrapper.frames.banner) {
                return;
            }

            switch (event.data.event) {
                case 'init':
                    initMraid(event.source);
                    break;
                case 'open':
                    mraid.open(event.data.data);
                    break;
                case 'close':
                    mraid.close();
                    break;
                case 'setExpandProperties':
                    mraid.setExpandProperties(event.data.data);
                    break;
                case 'setOrientationProperties':
                    mraid.setOrientationProperties(event.data.data);
                    break;
                case 'setResizeProperties':
                    mraid.setResizeProperties(event.data.data);
                    break;
                case 'useCustomClose':
                    mraid.useCustomClose(event.data.data);
                    break;
                case 'storePicture':
                    mraid.storePicture(event.data.data);
                    break;
                case 'createCalendarEvent':
                    mraid.createCalendarEvent(event.data.data);
                    break;
                case 'playVideo':
                    mraid.playVideo(event.data.data);
                    break;
            }
        });
    })()
</script>
